long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows the listing of specific plex software icons and adds a shortcut to execute and save sprocs in  SDE. 
In SDE press F5 to execute your procedure or Ctrl+S to save it
In VP designer, simply click on the drop down menu (top right) to get a reference list of icons.
